videos.headline: BYU's Hall tosses a 35-yard TD pass
videos.description: Jaren Hall, BYU's first black starting QB, throws a 35-yard touchdown pass to Dax Milne, who catches the ball with one hand to put the Cougars up 10-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU’s Hall tosses a 35-yard TD pass) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Hall runs for 29-yard TD
videos.description: Jaren Hall fakes the handoff then runs 29 yards for a BYU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU's Hall runs for 29-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCloud's 2-yard TD run puts USF within 2
videos.description: Jordan McCloud runs in a two-yard touchdown, cutting BYU's lead to 23-21.
